author: Steve
title: Steve
text:
I like the site because it makes creating a corporate identity easy. The down side is they are generic; so in the big league copyright might blow it. (Unless I automatically own the copyright to my logo and website).
I thought the merchandise ideas were also very good. One - Stop - Shop idea. Very good idea.
Quality.
Well, I thought the sweat shirt was too small, I.e. Short fitting. I guess I must be extra large. (I ordered large).
Base ball cap. The cap is okay, but the price is high in my opinion. 12â‚¬ would be fair, but you know your costs.
Mugs. No complaints; fair price and good quality.
My business experience was a good one. I would buy from you again.
Best regards
